# Data Deletion Policy

## How to Request Data Deletion

If you wish to delete your account and associated data, follow these steps:

1. **In-App Request:** Go to account settings and select "Delete My Account".
2. **Email Request:** Contact us at **[Your Email]** with the subject "Data Deletion Request".
3. **Manual Deletion:** If you signed up via Google or Facebook, revoke access through their settings.

Once we receive your request, we will process it within 7 days.

For any queries, email us at usamaijaz2119@gmail.com.

